name: CFStreamErrorHTTP
desc: Error codes that a read stream for an HTTP request may return.

items.name: case parseFailure
items.desc: A parsing error occurred while an incoming message was being deserialized and appended to a message object. The headers of the incoming message may be formatted improperly.

items.name: case redirectionLoop
items.desc: A redirection loop has been detected.

items.name: case badURL
items.desc: The URL is not properly formatted.
